  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary aim is to develop, and test the feasibility, of a novel and protocol-based
      cognitive behaviour therapy (CBT) treatment for body dysmorphic disorder (BDD) administered
      via the Internet.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
